An interface is blueprint of the Class  and  it has static constants , abstract methods.

The interface in java is a mechanism to acheive the abstraction . There can be only abstract methods , not method body.

It is used a acheive Multiple inheritance.


Why we used the interface :-

    :-  it is used to acheive abstraction.
    :- By, interface  we can support the funtionality of multiple inheritance

    :- It can be used to acheive loose coupling.